      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PUNCH DRUNK LOVE (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (19.67) at Healesville. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Key chance in this line up. PAW FERNA (3) was below best last time finishing seventh at Shepparton, but prior to that had been racing well including a Bottom Up - Grade 6 win two back at Healesville. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MOTIVATE (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at Shepparton in a handy 25.64 beating Auntie Amber. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances again. DOOKIE GIBLET (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
